Package com.github.jonathanxd.iutils.exception

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ArraySizeException
    Occurs when array size does not matches the size condition.
    CannotCollectElementsException
    Occurs when fails to grab elements.
    ExcludedElementIndexException
    Occurs when tries to grab a excluded element.
    FullListException
    Occurs when you try to add an element to a full size list.
    JStringApplyException
    Occurs when JStringUtil fails to process a string.
    LazyEvaluationException
    Occurs when a exception is thrown during a Lazy Evaluation.
    LimitExceededException
    Occurs when you try to add more elements than a sized list can carry.
    MaxRecursiveParseException
    Occurs when a parsing process exceeded the allowed limit of recursion.
    RethrowException
    Rethrow exception.
    TypeResolutionException
    Occurs when a type fails to be resolved by a type resolver.
